DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

98-2659. Disciplinary Counsel v. Mazer.

On August 25, 1999, respondent filed an affidavit of compliance. The affidavit did not include the certificate of service required by S.CtPrac.R. XIV(2)(C). Accordingly,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that respondent’s affidavit of compliance be, and hereby is, stricken.
